name: Diversified Staked ETH
public_notice: Anyone can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: The Diversified Staked ETH Index (dsETH) is an index token of the leading Ethereum liquid staking tokens. Along with providing a source of diversified staking yield, dsETH strengthens the Ethereum network with weightings that favor decentralized liquid staking protocols.
